\"}\",出现次数:3\naiops-k8s-08,frontend,frontend-2,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = shipping quote failure: failed to get shipping quote: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.27.213:50051: i/o timeout\\\"\"\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"0fe58837-fd9e-4985-8221-9bb9399d2a7b\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart/checkout\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"84c93109-cf0c-4fe5-ba02-7e422387364d\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-19T07:16:42.46548398Z\"\"}\",出现次数:3\naiops-k8s-04,frontend,frontend-0,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = shipping quote failure: failed to get shipping quote: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.27.213:50051: i/o timeout\\\"\"\"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"1fda5543-051b-4a73-8751-6223ce2efeef\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"POST\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/cart/checkout\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"request error\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"3a5564d9-3f8d-4dc1-a6ac-54c8ef618f2e\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"error\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-19T07:25:41.9442623Z\"\"}\",出现次数:3\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["frontend-2", "frontend-0", "frontend-1"], "service_name": ["frontend"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-08", "aiops-k8s-04", "aiops-k8s-01"]}, "matched_anomaly": "Please analyze the abnormal event between 2025-06-19T07:10:21Z and 2025-06-19T07:33:21Z and provide the root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-19 07:10:21+00:00 to 2025-06-19 07:33:21+00:00"}, "trace_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的链路追踪数据，我现在对异常事件进行分析。从数据中可以清晰地看到故障的根本原因。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"error_ratio\", \"checkoutservice->shippingservice\", \"frontend->checkoutservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"shippingservice 出现严重的连接超时错误：'dial tcp 10.233.27.213:50051: i/o timeout' 和 'timed out waiting for server handshake'，错误次数达220次\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\", \n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice 调用 shippingservice 的延迟从正常 9.3秒 激增至 26.9秒，延迟倍数约28.8倍\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\", \n      \"evidence\": \"frontend 因下游 checkoutservice 故障而出现大量 HTTP 500 错误，错误传播至用户端\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 根因分析总结\n\n**根本原因**: `shippingservice` 服务不可用，导致连接超时错误。\n\n**故障传播路径**:\n1. **根因**: `shippingservice` 无法响应请求，出现 TCP 连接超时\n2. **直接影响**: `checkoutservice` 调用 `shippingservice` 的 GetQuote 和 ShipOrder 操作全部超时\n3. **连锁反应**: `frontend` 调用 `checkoutservice` 的 PlaceOrder 操作失败，返回 HTTP 500 错误\n4. **用户影响**: 结账流程完全中断\n\n**关键指标**:\n- shippingservice 连接超时错误：220次\n- checkoutservice 延迟激增：28.8倍\n- frontend HTTP 500 错误：280次\n\n故障是由于 shippingservice 的网络连接问题或服务本身不可用导致的级联故障。", "log_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的日志数据，我已经完成了对异常事件的分析。以下是详细的分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"transport\", \"Error while dialing\", \"i/o timeout\", \"timed out waiting for server handshake\", \"connection error\", \"context canceled\", \"Unavailable\", \"Internal\", \"Canceled\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"shippingservice服务出现连接超时和网络不可用问题，表现为i/o timeout和timed out waiting for server handshake错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to get shipping quote: rpc error: code = Unavailable desc = connection error: desc = \\\"transport: Error while dialing dial tcp 10.233.27.213:50051: i/o timeout\\\"\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"frontend服务在调用shippingservice时遇到网络连接问题，导致上下文取消和内部错误\",\n      \"evidence\": \"failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Canceled desc = context canceled 和 failed to complete the order: rpc error: code = Internal desc = shipping quote failure\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 分析总结\n\n**主要发现：**\n1. **故障模式**: 所有错误日志都来自frontend服务的三个实例（frontend-0, frontend-1, frontend-2），涉及购物车结算流程\n2. **根因服务**: shippingservice（IP地址：10.233.27.213:50051）出现严重网络连接问题\n3. **错误类型**: \n   - I/O超时（i/o timeout）\n   - 服务器握手超时（timed out waiting for server handshake）\n   - 连接错误（connection error）\n   - 上下文取消（context canceled）\n\n**关键证据：**\n- 错误集中在2025-06-19T07:10:48Z至07:25:41Z时间段\n- 所有frontend实例都报告了相同的shippingservice连接问题\n- 错误频次很高（最高出现47次），表明是持续性故障\n\n**建议**: shippingservice的网络连接或服务可用性问题是本次异常的根本原因，需要检查该服务的网络配置、资源使用情况和健康状态。", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的监控数据，我来分析异常事件期间的指标变化。从数据可以看出，系统在2025-06-19T07:10:21Z到2025-06-19T07:33:21Z期间出现了明显的性能问题。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"rrt\", \"error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"memory_usage\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"shippingservice-0 Pod出现严重性能问题和错误率激增，rrt_max从6260.12飙升至10319152.3，error_ratio从0.0升至50.85\",\n      \"evidence\": \"shippingservice-0的rrt_max变化率199.76%，error_ratio从0.0升至50.85，表明该Pod存在严重性能瓶颈\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend服务\",\n      \"reason\": \"所有frontend Pod实例均出现rrt_max和error_ratio异常，rrt_max从约400,000飙升至60,000,000+\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend-0/1/2的rrt_max变化率均超过197%，server_error_ratio从0.0升至0.3左右，表明前端服务整体性能下降\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"checkoutservice-2 Pod的rrt和rrt_max出现显著增长，rrt从7695.97升至925703.24\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice-2的rrt变化率196.7%，rrt_max变化率195.31%，表明该Pod处理能力严重下降\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tidb\",\n      \"reason\": \"tidb数据库内存使用率上升，memory_usage从649756672.0升至737087488.0\",\n      \"evidence\": \"tidb-tidb的memory_usage变化率12.59%，可能影响数据库性能并间接导致上游服务延迟\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现**：\n1. **shippingservice-0**是问题最严重的组件，错误率高达50